 replace him with either Empath or Blackfang, or even one of&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; the new guys around.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus holds her close, tickling her, while he takes care of&lt;BR&gt;&gt; business.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; He opens a comm.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: Yggdrasil, what&#39;s the status of that team?&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Airshadow Nightstar &lt;airly2002@h...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Elita:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Elita continued giggling and laughting. She was enjoying a lot&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; playing with her daddy. She was having a lot fun and if she would be a&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; little older, she would have wished that it never ends.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt;Subject: Re: Daddy &gt;Date: Sat, 10 May 2003 21:59:17 -0700 (PDT) &gt; &gt;:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; : Rodimus Prime : : &gt;Rodimus was having fun playing with his daughter,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; but his thoughts started to dwell on Nightlight. He wished she was&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; there so they could all be together as a family. &gt; &gt;Rodimus tossed&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Elita up just a little bit, then cought her. &gt; &gt; &gt;Airshadow Nightstar&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; wrote: &gt;Elita: &gt; &gt;Elita Laughtes Aloud, that was such fun. She was&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; gigglig pleaced while she spread her little arms toward her dad &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;From: Richard Allen &gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;To:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;Subject: Re: Daddy &gt;Date: Sat, 10 May 2003&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; 21:2